Github Copilot is a supporting AI tool for software developers. It is similar to Codeium tool

As a developer you should have:
- Visual Studio Code 
- Search on youtube.com for videos on how to sign up an account (on github) and how to install into your Visual Studio Code
- Basically Github Copilot will support you coding eg:
  + write directly functions if you like
  + chat with you where you can give an idea and then i will write code for you
  + documentation for your functions

# Useful videos on youtube.com
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SLMfhuptCo8
